From 423f390e768aa6a2088a955fb8d9602a0bbc94b7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ashwant Krishna R <ashwantk@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sun, 3 Aug 2025 16:09:35 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:CP:wifi: ath12k: Add missing htt stats

Add missing FW stats to HTT stats type 12, 17, 18, 22 and 59.
Do cosmetic changes on HTT stat type 1.
Add new stats tag - HTT_STATS_TX_PDEV_BE_UL_MU_OFDMA_STATS_TAG,
HTT_STATS_TX_PDEV_BE_DL_MU_OFDMA_STATS_TAG for these HTT stats types.

Patch-dependency: ath12k/0280-0001-wifi-ath12k-Add-debugfs-support.patch
Patch-work: None

Signed-off-by: Ashwant Krishna R <ashwantk@qti.qualcomm.com>
